    <name>DINOS Random Dataset Creator</name>
    
    <shortDescription>
		Creates random bogus datasets for use in DINOS testing
    </shortDescription>
    
    <fullDescription>
    
        <intro>
        	<br/>
        	 Creates a random bogus set for use in DINOS with:
			 <br/>
			 1 - A column of every supported type of data. The columns are shuffled each time and have random data.
			 <br/>
			 2 - A column of the target data type chosen in the dialogue
			 <br/>
			 3 - Flow variables for automatically setting
			<br/>
		</intro>
        
        
        <option name="short name of first option (like in the dialog)">description of first option</option>
        <option name="short name of second option (like in the dialog)">description of second option</option>
